title: Cafe Flore
typeOfFood: Lacto, Ovo, Japanese, Beer/Wine, Take-out, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Vegetarian and macrobiotic cuisine catered for upon reservation - but reported not vegan suitable (Apr 2015). Can be all organic upon request (need reserve 1 week ahead). Also lunch boxes for macrobiotics. Owner understands basic English and French. At 岐阜県高山市相生町37.
